# 🚀 Full Stack Auth Dashboard

A complete full-stack web application with **User Authentication**, **JWT Security**, and a **User Management Dashboard** built using Node.js, Express, MongoDB Atlas, and Vanilla JavaScript (Axios).

---

## 🌐 Live Demo

* 🔗 Frontend (GitHub Pages):
  https://chamithkumar.github.io/auth-dashboard/

* 🔗 Backend (Render):
  https://auth-api-tvca.onrender.com/

---

## 📌 Features

### 🔐 Authentication

* User Signup with hashed password (bcrypt)
* User Login with JWT token
* Secure authentication using JSON Web Tokens
* Logout functionality with token removal

### 🛡️ Authorization

* Role-based access (Admin/User)
* Protected routes using middleware
* Admin-only route access

### 👤 User Management

* Add new users
* View all users (protected)
* Edit user details
* Delete users
* Search users in real-time

### 🌍 Deployment

* Frontend deployed on **GitHub Pages**
* Backend deployed on **Render**
* Database hosted on **MongoDB Atlas**

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Frontend

* HTML
* JavaScript (Vanilla)
* Axios

### Backend

* Node.js
* Express.js

### Database

* MongoDB Atlas
* Mongoose

### Authentication

* bcryptjs
* jsonwebtoken (JWT)

